OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fmostly fading during this evening,
OL,7,Fleaving a largely dry night with some
OL,8,Fclear spells, especially towards the
OL,9,Feast. The odd shower still possible in
OL,10,Fthe west, with some mist and fog
OL,11,Fpatches developing elsewhere towards
OL,12,Fdawn.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FA bright start in the east,
OL,15,Fotherwise a good deal of cloud around
OL,16,Fwith only limited bright spells.
OL,17,FLargely dry, except for a few showers
OL,18,Fin the west. Feeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
